<topic template="Default" modified="2026-04-07T16:41:36.903Z" lasteditedby="noorhbo" version="2" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title>2.6.2 Inching Operation</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Input unit: 1/1000° or 1/1000 mm. Decimal point input is also supported. Ex: When “2.” is entered, set</keyword>
    <keyword>Movement is not performed unless all conditions for the respective operation are satisfied. The maintenance error message showing the reason of interlock is displayed on the Output Line of this screen. (Refer to Figure 2.2)</keyword>
    <keyword>NOTES-</keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading4">寸进操作</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;">通过这种操作，可以对弹夹轴进行移动。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="line-height:1.50;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">操作步骤</text></para>
    <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px; font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">打开维护模式。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;"><text styleclass="Notes">按</text><text style="font-weight:bold;">[</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">¬</text><text style="font-weight:bold;">]</text><text styleclass="Notes">或</text><text style="font-weight:bold;">[</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">®</text><text style="font-weight:bold;">]</text><text styleclass="Notes">光标键选择 FEED MODE:INCH。所选模式将以黄色高亮显示。</text></li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">按下<text style="font-weight:bold;">[</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">¬</text><text style="font-weight:bold;">]</text>或<text style="font-weight:bold;">[</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">®</text><text style="font-weight:bold;">]</text>光标键，选择进纸超控，此时料盒需要旋转 100%/50%/25%/0%。所选模式将以黄色高亮显示。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">在英寸数据字段中输入英寸数据量。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:10px; margin-left:24px;">要移动刀库轴，按操作面板上的<text style="font-weight:bold;">[+]</text>按钮顺时针移动，或按<text style="font-weight:bold;">[-]</text>按钮逆时针移动。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-left:24px;">可通过此屏幕上的ATC 职位显示屏观察轴的实际移动情况。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Notes" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:5px; margin-left:24px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">-注-</text></para>
    <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Notes" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:5px; margin-left:24px; font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Notes" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-bottom:5px; margin-left:24px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">除非满足相应操作的所有条件，否则不会执行移动。显示联锁原因的维护错误信息将显示在此屏幕的输出行</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;">[</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">¬</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;">]</text><text styleclass="Normal"> 或 </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;">[</text><text styleclass="" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">®</text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;">]</text><text style="font-size:10pt;">上（参照 </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="false" type="topiclink" href="2_6-Moving-Magazine-Servo-Axis" anchor="Fig2.2" target="_blank" style="font-size:10pt; color:#0000ff;">图 2.2</link><text style="font-size:10pt;">）</text><text styleclass="Normal"> 。 </text></li>
      <li styleclass="Notes" style="text-indent:-24px; margin-left:24px;"><text style="font-size:10pt;">输入单位：1/1000° 或 1/1000 mm。也支持小数点输入。例如：输入 &quot;2. &quot;时，设定值为 &quot;2.000&quot;。</text></li>
    </list>
  </body>
</topic>
